---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, COMPANY_NAME } from '../consts';
---

<BaseHead title={`About Us - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Hermetrix Technologies is a New Zealand-based cybersecurity company specializing in secure communications and compliance guidance for the Asia-Pacific region." />

<Header />
<main>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>About Hermetrix Technologies</h1>
			<p class="tagline">Building Trust Through Security Expertise</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="mission">
				<h2>Our Mission</h2>
				<p>Hermetrix Technologies exists to provide organizations across the Asia-Pacific region with access to certified security solutions and expert guidance. We bridge the gap between complex security requirements and practical, implementable solutions.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="story">
				<h2>Our Focus</h2>
				<p>Founded in New Zealand, Hermetrix Technologies recognizes the unique security challenges faced by organizations in the APAC region. We specialize in understanding both international security standards and local compliance frameworks to provide relevant, effective security guidance.</p>
				
				<p>Our approach is built on three core principles:</p>
				
				<div class="principles">
					<div class="principle">
						<h3>Security-First Mindset</h3>
						<p>Every solution we recommend or implement is evaluated against its security merits and certification status first.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="principle">
						<h3>Practical Guidance</h3>
						<p>We focus on helping organizations understand and work toward security goals through achievable steps and appropriate solutions.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="principle">
						<h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
						<p>The security landscape evolves constantly. We maintain our expertise to provide current, relevant advice.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="values">
				<h2>Our Values</h2>
				<div class="values-grid">
					<div class="value">
						<h3>Integrity</h3>
						<p>We provide honest assessments and recommendations based on security needs, not sales targets.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="value">
						<h3>Expertise</h3>
						<p>We maintain deep knowledge of security frameworks, standards, and certified technologies.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="value">
						<h3>Discretion</h3>
						<p>We understand the sensitive nature of security work and maintain strict confidentiality.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="value">
						<h3>Excellence</h3>
						<p>We strive to deliver exceptional service and support in everything we do.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="approach">
				<h2>Our Approach to Security</h2>
				<p>At Hermetrix Technologies, we believe effective security requires understanding both the technical requirements and the operational context. We help organizations:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Understand complex security frameworks like NZISM and PSR</li>
					<li>Identify appropriate certified security products</li>
					<li>Implement solutions that balance security and usability</li>
					<li>Develop sustainable security practices</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="disclaimer">
				<h3>Our Commitment to Transparency</h3>
				<p><strong>Hermetrix Technologies is a registered New Zealand company providing security consulting and implementation services.</strong> We are not a government agency and cannot provide official security clearances or compliance certifications.</p>
				<p>We work with commercially available, certified security products and provide guidance to help organizations navigate security requirements. Official certifications and formal compliance status must be obtained through appropriate government channels.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section">
				<h2>Ready to Enhance Your Security?</h2>
				<p>Contact us to discuss how we can help your organization achieve its security objectives.</p>
				<div class="contact-methods">
					<a href="mailto:hello@hermetrix.nz" class="btn primary">Get in Touch</a>
					<a href="/services" class="btn secondary">Our Services</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>
<Footer />

<style>
body {
	margin: 0;
	min-height: 100vh;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
	line-height: 1.6;
}

main {
	flex: 1;
}

	/* Hero Section */
	.hero {
	padding: 4rem 2rem;
	text-align: center;
	background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1419 0%, #1a365d 50%, #2d3748 100%);
	color: white;
	position: relative;
	overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::before {
	content: "";
	position: absolute;
	top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
	background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg width="100%25" height="100%25" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle fill="%2363b3ed" fill-opacity="0.05" cx="10%25" cy="20%25" r="80"/><circle fill="%2363b3ed" fill-opacity="0.03" cx="80%25" cy="70%25" r="120"/><circle fill="%2390cdf4" fill-opacity="0.04" cx="50%25" cy="50%25" r="100"/></svg>');
	z-index: 0;
}
.hero > .container {
	position: relative;
	z-index: 1;
	}

	.hero h1 {
					font-size: 4rem;
					margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
					font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Segoe UI', 'Arial Black', Arial, sans-serif;
					font-weight: 900;
					color: #ffffff;
					text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 2px 0 #1a365d;
					letter-spacing: 0.02em;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #90cdf4;
	}

	.about-content {
		padding: 4rem 1rem;
		background: white;
	}

	.mission {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
	}

	.mission h2 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 2rem;
	}

	.mission p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #4a5568;
	}

	.story {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
	}

	.story h2 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.story p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.principles {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.principle {
		background: #f8fafc;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		border-left: 4px solid #1a365d;
	}

	.principle h3 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}

	.values {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
	}

	.values h2 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.values-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.value {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem 1rem;
	}

	.value h3 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}

	.approach {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
	}

	.approach h2 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.approach ul {
		margin: 1.5rem 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}

	.approach li {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.disclaimer {
		background: #fffaf0;
		border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
		border-left: 4px solid #ed8936;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		margin: 3rem auto;
		max-width: 800px;
	}

	.disclaimer h3 {
		color: #c05621;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.disclaimer p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		background: #1a365d;
		color: white;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.cta-section h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.contact-methods {
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
		margin: 0 0.5rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 0.375rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background-color: #90cdf4;
		color: #1a365d;
	}

	.btn.primary:hover {
		background-color: #63b3ed;
	}

	.btn.secondary {
		background-color: transparent;
		color: #90cdf4;
		border: 2px solid #90cdf4;
	}

	.btn.secondary:hover {
		background-color: #90cdf4;
		color: #1a365d;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* Mobile responsiveness */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.contact-methods {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1rem;
		}
		
		.btn {
			margin: 0;
		}

		.principles,
		.values-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
